# Gemini Code Assist: Exclude heavy directories to prevent RAG cache death spiral
# Root cause: GCA indexing package.json files across monorepo → 52% CPU → extension host freeze

# Package managers & dependencies
**/node_modules/**
**/.pnpm-store/**
**/bower_components/**

# Python environments
**/.venv/**
**/venv/**
**/__pycache__/**
**/.tox/**
**/*.egg-info/**

# Build artifacts
**/.next/**
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/out/**
**/.turbo/**

# Version control internals
**/.git/**

# Large media & binaries
**/*.mp4
**/*.webm
**/*.pdf
**/*.zip
**/*.tar.gz
**/*.whl
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.so
**/*.dylib

# Database & caches
**/.firebase/**
**/.lancedb/**
**/*.sqlite3
**/state.vscdb*
**/.cache/**
**/.gradle/**

# Monorepo heavy zones
**/external_repos/**
**/legacy_workspaces/**
**/external_payloads/**
**/devrel-demos/**
**/deep-archive/**

# AiYou stack (many nested package.json files — RAG cache thrash source)
**/aiyou_stack/aiyou-fastapi-services/apps/**/node_modules/**
**/aiyou_stack/aiyou-fastapi-services/infrastructure/**
**/aiyou_stack/cosmic-crab-payload/node_modules/**
**/aiyou_stack/nascent-apollo/node_modules/**

# Secrets
.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.production
